♪ ♪

00:00:21.309 --> 00:00:23.179
[woman singing in Japanese]

00:00:23.179 --> 00:00:28.691
♪ ♪

00:01:42.539 --> 00:01:44.075
&gt;&gt; narrator: THIS IS THE TALE OF

00:01:44.075 --> 00:01:45.444
A MAN WHO CONTINUES TO SEARCH

00:01:45.444 --> 00:01:47.782
FOR HIS OWN PATH, EVEN AS FATE

00:01:47.782 --> 00:01:49.720
BETRAYS HIM.

00:01:49.720 --> 00:01:51.255
THE WAR BETWEEN THE SPIRAL RACES

00:01:51.255 --> 00:01:53.861
AND THE ANTI‐SPIRAL RACE...

00:01:53.861 --> 00:01:55.464
THIS WAS THE ROOT CAUSE

00:01:55.464 --> 00:01:57.234
OF EVERYTHING.

00:01:57.234 --> 00:01:58.504
IN ORDER TO EXTERMINATE

00:01:58.504 --> 00:02:00.742
HUMANITY, THE ANTI‐SPIRALS SENT

00:02:00.742 --> 00:02:01.744
THE MOON PLUMMETING

00:02:01.744 --> 00:02:02.879
TOWARDS EARTH.

00:02:02.879 --> 00:02:04.683
IT WAS SIMON AND HIS FELLOW TEAM

00:02:04.683 --> 00:02:06.119
GURREN MEMBERS WHO TRIGGERED

00:02:06.119 --> 00:02:06.887
THIS CALAMITY.

00:02:06.887 --> 00:02:08.691
WILL THEIR STRUGGLE FOR FREEDOM

00:02:08.691 --> 00:02:10.662
LEAD TO MANKIND’S DOWNFALL?

00:02:10.662 --> 00:02:13.266
HAVING LOST NIA, SIMON IS

00:02:13.266 --> 00:02:14.703
SHACKLED BY THE HANDCUFFS

00:02:14.703 --> 00:02:16.139
OF DESPAIR.

00:02:23.453 --> 00:02:27.161
[crowd clamoring]

00:02:27.161 --> 00:02:28.731
&gt;&gt; GIVE US SIMON!

00:02:28.731 --> 00:02:31.537
&gt;&gt; MAKE HIM PAY FOR WHAT HE DID!

00:02:31.537 --> 00:02:33.908
&gt;&gt; HE WAS NEVER A HERO!

00:02:33.908 --> 00:02:36.145
&gt;&gt; SIMON IS THE CAUSE OF

00:02:36.145 --> 00:02:37.147
ALL THIS!

00:02:37.147 --> 00:02:38.450
&gt;&gt; IT’S ALL THAT SIMON’S FAULT

00:02:38.450 --> 00:02:39.686
THAT THE MOON IS GOING TO FALL

00:02:39.686 --> 00:02:41.356
ON US!

00:02:50.875 --> 00:02:52.779
&gt;&gt; Simon: ROSSIU...

00:02:52.779 --> 00:02:54.549
TELL ME WHY.

00:02:54.549 --> 00:02:55.651
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: THE CITIZENS WHO WERE

00:02:55.651 --> 00:02:57.254
EVACUATED TO THE PARLIAMENT

00:02:57.254 --> 00:03:00.227
TOWER HAD BEGUN TO RIOT.

00:03:00.227 --> 00:03:01.262
THEY SAY OUR DEFEAT OF

00:03:01.262 --> 00:03:01.930
LORDGENOME IS WHAT SET THIS

00:03:01.930 --> 00:03:03.901
CATASTROPHE IN MOTION

00:03:03.901 --> 00:03:05.237
AND THAT TEAM DAI‐GURREN IS TO

00:03:05.237 --> 00:03:06.472
BLAME FOR THE MOON FALLING

00:03:06.472 --> 00:03:07.307
FROM THE SKY.

00:03:07.307 --> 00:03:08.711
THE PEOPLE ARE DIRECTING THEIR

00:03:08.711 --> 00:03:10.615
ANGER AT THE NEW GOVERNMENT.

00:03:10.615 --> 00:03:12.886
YOUR CONVERSATION WITH NIA WAS

00:03:12.886 --> 00:03:14.221
BROADCAST LIVE ACROSS

00:03:14.221 --> 00:03:15.625
THE WORLD.

00:03:15.625 --> 00:03:17.595
EVERY CITIZEN NOW KNOWS THAT THE

00:03:17.595 --> 00:03:18.731
MOON WILL SLAM INTO THE EARTH

00:03:18.731 --> 00:03:20.702
IN THREE WEEKS’ TIME.

00:03:20.702 --> 00:03:22.237
ALSO THE ENTIRE CITY WAS PRIVY

00:03:22.237 --> 00:03:23.774
TO YOUR FOOLISH AND RECKLESS

00:03:23.774 --> 00:03:24.843
FIGHT EARLIER.

00:03:24.843 --> 00:03:26.479
I CAN NO LONGER PROTECT YOU.

00:03:26.479 --> 00:03:30.187
&gt;&gt; Simon: PROTECT ME?

00:03:30.187 --> 00:03:31.222
&gt;&gt; THIS IS THE GUY!

00:03:31.222 --> 00:03:32.291
IT’S ALL HIS FAULT!

00:03:32.291 --> 00:03:35.464
&gt;&gt; TEAR IT DOWN!

00:03:42.812 --> 00:03:44.248
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: IN THE EYES OF THE

00:03:44.248 --> 00:03:45.518
CITIZENS, YOU ARE NOW NO

00:03:45.518 --> 00:03:46.319
DIFFERENT FROM LORDGENOME,

00:03:46.319 --> 00:03:49.325
SIMON, IN WHICH CASE, WE MUST

00:03:49.325 --> 00:03:50.862
PUNISH YOU IN THE SAME MANNER,

00:03:50.862 --> 00:03:52.331
EXACTLY AS WE DID WITH

00:03:52.331 --> 00:03:54.201
LORDGENOME TO CONTAIN OUR ANGER

00:03:54.201 --> 00:03:55.571
BACK THEN.

00:03:55.571 --> 00:03:57.642
[metal clanking]

00:03:57.642 --> 00:04:00.447
[door slams]

00:04:00.447 --> 00:04:02.685
PLEASE WAIT HERE UNTIL IT IS

00:04:02.685 --> 00:04:03.721
TIME FOR YOUR TRIAL.

00:04:03.721 --> 00:04:04.723
&gt;&gt; Simon: TRIAL?

00:04:04.723 --> 00:04:05.892
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: WE ARE NOW A NATION

00:04:05.892 --> 00:04:07.294
OF LAWS.

00:04:07.294 --> 00:04:08.731
QUESTIONS OF WAR CRIMES ARE TO

00:04:08.731 --> 00:04:10.300
BE SETTLED IN A TRIAL.

00:04:10.300 --> 00:04:11.002
&gt;&gt; Simon: FIRST IT WAS

00:04:11.002 --> 00:04:11.670
GOD’S RULES.

00:04:11.670 --> 00:04:12.739
NOW IT’S THE LAW.

00:04:12.739 --> 00:04:14.275
YOU’RE A MAN WHO LOVES TO BE

00:04:14.275 --> 00:04:15.578
TIED DOWN, AREN’T YOU?

00:04:15.578 --> 00:04:17.314
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: WE HAVE ALWAYS MADE

00:04:17.314 --> 00:04:18.383
PROGRESS ON THE SACRIFICES OF

00:04:18.383 --> 00:04:19.753
THE THOSE WHO CAME BEFORE US.

00:04:19.753 --> 00:04:21.523
LIKE MY MOTHER...

00:04:21.523 --> 00:04:22.692
AND KAMINA.

00:04:22.692 --> 00:04:24.395
&gt;&gt; Simon: WHAT?

00:04:24.395 --> 00:04:25.665
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: IT’S TRUE,

00:04:25.665 --> 00:04:27.000
KAMINA’S DEATH MADE US ALL

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:27.635
A LOT STRONGER.

00:04:27.635 --> 00:04:29.371
IT WAS THANKS TO HIS SACRIFICE

00:04:29.371 --> 00:04:31.510
THAT WE WON THAT BATTLE.

00:04:31.510 --> 00:04:33.313
&gt;&gt; Simon: HOLD IT RIGHT THERE.

00:04:33.313 --> 00:04:34.482
ARE YOU TRYING TO TELL ME

00:04:34.482 --> 00:04:35.518
THAT IT’S A GOOD THING THAT

00:04:35.518 --> 00:04:37.755
MY BRO DIED?

00:04:37.755 --> 00:04:39.291
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: BASED ON THE OUTCOME,

00:04:39.291 --> 00:04:41.830
THEN YES, I AM.

00:04:41.830 --> 00:04:43.266
&gt;&gt; Simon: JUST SHUT UP!

00:04:43.266 --> 00:04:44.603
IN CASE YOU DIDN’T KNOW, THERE’S

00:04:44.603 --> 00:04:45.905
JUST SOME THINGS YOU CAN’T SAY!

00:04:45.905 --> 00:04:47.542
YOU BASTARD! HEY!

00:04:47.542 --> 00:04:50.380
DO YOU REALLY THINK THAT?!

00:04:50.380 --> 00:04:52.384
[Simon grunting]

00:04:52.384 --> 00:04:53.386
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: YOU ARE EXACTLY LIKE

00:04:53.386 --> 00:04:55.490
KAMINA WAS IN THE OLD DAYS.

00:04:55.490 --> 00:04:56.459
HAVE YOU LEARNED NOTHING FROM

00:04:56.459 --> 00:04:56.860
HIS DEATH?

00:04:56.860 --> 00:05:01.670
YOU HAVEN’T GROWN AT ALL.

00:05:01.670 --> 00:05:03.741
I WILL KEEP YOUR CORE DRILL.

00:05:03.741 --> 00:05:06.312
IT’S IRONIC, THE SOURCE OF

00:05:06.312 --> 00:05:07.615
YOUR POWER WAS THE SEED OF

00:05:07.615 --> 00:05:10.320
MANKIND’S DESTRUCTION.

00:05:10.320 --> 00:05:11.957
&gt;&gt; Simon: ROSSIU, YOU WILL NEVER

00:05:11.957 --> 00:05:13.727
UNDERSTAND WHAT BRO FELT INSIDE

00:05:13.727 --> 00:05:16.032
OR WHAT HIS DEATH GAVE

00:05:16.032 --> 00:05:19.471
TO ALL OF US.

00:05:19.471 --> 00:05:21.475
HEH. THAT LOOK IN YOUR EYES...

00:05:21.475 --> 00:05:23.079
IT’S EXACTLY THE SAME LOOK THAT

00:05:23.079 --> 00:05:24.583
PRIEST BACK IN ADAI VILLAGE HAD

00:05:24.583 --> 00:05:28.389
IN HIS EYES.

00:05:28.389 --> 00:05:29.559
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: IT IS YOU WHO

00:05:29.559 --> 00:05:31.530
UNDERSTANDS NOTHING, SIMON.

00:05:31.530 --> 00:05:33.433
SEVEN YEARS, AND YOU HAVEN’T

00:05:33.433 --> 00:05:35.370
EVEN TRIED TO CHANGE.

00:05:35.370 --> 00:05:38.009
YOU’RE THE ONE.

00:05:40.648 --> 00:05:42.552
&gt;&gt; Kiyal: SO IS IT TRUE WHAT

00:05:42.552 --> 00:05:42.986
THEY’RE SAYING?

00:05:42.986 --> 00:05:44.388
DID THEY REALLY ARREST SIMON?

00:05:44.388 --> 00:05:45.390
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: IT’S TRUE.

00:05:45.390 --> 00:05:46.359
&gt;&gt; Kiyal: WHY WOULD THEY DO

00:05:46.359 --> 00:05:47.361
THAT?

00:05:47.361 --> 00:05:47.996
THAT IS SO MESSED UP!

00:05:47.996 --> 00:05:49.465
THAT JERK ROSSIU’S GONE

00:05:49.465 --> 00:05:50.400
TOTALLY CRAZY!

00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:51.537
&gt;&gt; Kiyoh: KIYAL, DON’T SHOUT

00:05:51.537 --> 00:05:52.839
IN THE HOSPITAL.

00:05:52.839 --> 00:05:53.541
&gt;&gt; Kiyal: SORRY.

00:05:53.541 --> 00:05:54.341
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: ROSSIU’S MAKING

00:05:54.341 --> 00:05:55.110
A CERTAIN AMOUNT OF SENSE.

00:05:55.110 --> 00:05:56.613
AND MAYBE WHAT HE’S DONE TO

00:05:56.613 --> 00:05:57.749
SIMON IS JUST MEANT TO BE

00:05:57.749 --> 00:05:58.817
A TEMPORARY SOLUTION.

00:05:58.817 --> 00:05:59.819
&gt;&gt; Kiyal: HMPH!

00:05:59.819 --> 00:06:01.389
ROSSIU MIGHT HAVE COMMON SENSE,

00:06:01.389 --> 00:06:02.559
BUT HE’S SO COLDHEARTED.

00:06:02.559 --> 00:06:04.061
I REALLY CANNOT STAND THAT GUY.

00:06:04.061 --> 00:06:05.731
I HAVE NO IDEA WHAT THE HECK

00:06:05.731 --> 00:06:07.367
KINON SEES IN HIM.

00:06:07.367 --> 00:06:07.802
&gt;&gt; Kiyoh: KIYAL.

00:06:07.802 --> 00:06:08.671
&gt;&gt; Kiyal: YOU KNOW, I DON’T GIVE

00:06:08.671 --> 00:06:09.773
A DAMN HOW BUSY SHE IS.

00:06:09.773 --> 00:06:10.575
I REALLY DON’T.

00:06:10.575 --> 00:06:12.411
HOW CAN SHE NOT EVEN STOP BY

00:06:12.411 --> 00:06:13.379
TO SEE ANNE?

00:06:13.379 --> 00:06:14.348
KINON’S TOTALLY CHANGED, AND NOT

00:06:14.348 --> 00:06:15.350
FOR THE BETTER.

00:06:15.350 --> 00:06:16.520
&gt;&gt; Kiyoh: KIYAL!

00:06:16.520 --> 00:06:18.022
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: NOW, NOW, KIYAL.

00:06:18.022 --> 00:06:18.958
IT’S ONE THING TO TALK

00:06:18.958 --> 00:06:20.360
LIKE THAT IN HERE, BUT DON’T

00:06:20.360 --> 00:06:21.128
SAY THAT OUTSIDE.

00:06:21.128 --> 00:06:22.431
THESE DAYS, THERE’S NO TELLING

00:06:22.431 --> 00:06:24.435
WHAT MIGHT HAPPEN IF YOU SAY

00:06:24.435 --> 00:06:25.705
THE WRONG THING.

00:06:25.705 --> 00:06:28.577
[commotion and shouting]

00:06:28.577 --> 00:06:30.013
&gt;&gt; SEND OUT SIMON!

00:06:30.013 --> 00:06:31.382
THE GUY WHO’S RESPONSIBLE

00:06:31.382 --> 00:06:31.984
HAS TO PAY!

00:06:31.984 --> 00:06:33.019
&gt;&gt; YOU GOT A PLAN TO DEAL WITH

00:06:33.019 --> 00:06:33.988
THE MOON FALLING?!

00:06:33.988 --> 00:06:35.658
WHAT’S THE GOVERNMENT DOING?!

00:06:35.658 --> 00:06:37.127
&gt;&gt; GIVE ME BACK MY HOUSE!

00:06:37.127 --> 00:06:38.129
REIMBURSE ME!

00:06:38.129 --> 00:06:41.803
&gt;&gt; I WANT MY PEACEFUL LIFE BACK!

00:06:41.803 --> 00:06:42.739
&gt;&gt; Ron: THE MUGANN’S ENERGY

00:06:42.739 --> 00:06:44.108
BARRIER CAN BE BREACHED BY USING

00:06:44.108 --> 00:06:44.943
THE GIGA DRILL TO REFLECT ITS

00:06:44.943 --> 00:06:47.515
BEAM BACK AT IT.

00:06:47.515 --> 00:06:48.550
THE PROBLEM IS, HOW DO WE STOP

00:06:48.550 --> 00:06:50.721
THE BODY ITSELF FROM EXPLODING?

00:06:50.721 --> 00:06:52.424
[slurps]

00:06:52.424 --> 00:06:53.493
&gt;&gt; Darry: THIS ENEMY’S TRICKY.

00:06:53.493 --> 00:06:54.495
&gt;&gt; Gimmy: THE THING I STILL

00:06:54.495 --> 00:06:55.163
DON’T GET IS THAT THE GRAPEARLS

00:06:55.163 --> 00:06:56.934
ARE SUPERIOR TO GURREN LAGANN,

00:06:56.934 --> 00:06:57.502
AREN’T THEY?

00:06:57.502 --> 00:06:59.071
IT JUST DOESN’T SEEM RIGHT FOR

00:06:59.071 --> 00:07:00.006
THE PROTOTYPE TO BE

00:07:00.006 --> 00:07:00.775
MORE POWERFUL.

00:07:00.775 --> 00:07:01.743
&gt;&gt; Ron: GOODNESS!

00:07:01.743 --> 00:07:02.946
WHAT A THING TO SAY.

00:07:02.946 --> 00:07:03.948
OH, YOU.

00:07:03.948 --> 00:07:04.950
WHAT SHALL I DO TO CLOSE THAT

00:07:04.950 --> 00:07:07.522
MOUTH OF YOURS?

00:07:07.522 --> 00:07:09.024
&gt;&gt; Gimmy: SINCE I WAS A KID,

00:07:09.024 --> 00:07:10.427
THIS IS THE ONE GUY I CAN’T

00:07:10.427 --> 00:07:11.495
DEAL WITH.

00:07:11.495 --> 00:07:12.699
&gt;&gt; Tetsukan: WHAT ABOUT SIMON?

00:07:12.699 --> 00:07:13.634
WHAT DO YOU THINK’LL HAPPEN

00:07:13.634 --> 00:07:14.168
TO HIM?

00:07:14.168 --> 00:07:15.136
&gt;&gt; Ron: YOU MEAN HIS ARREST?

00:07:15.136 --> 00:07:15.871
&gt;&gt; Artenborough: WILL HE

00:07:15.871 --> 00:07:17.107
BE EXECUTED?!

00:07:17.107 --> 00:07:18.076
&gt;&gt; Gimmy: COME ON, ARTENBOROUGH.

00:07:18.076 --> 00:07:18.777
DON’T BE GETTING AHEAD

00:07:18.777 --> 00:07:19.178
OF YOURSELF.

00:07:19.178 --> 00:07:20.413
&gt;&gt; Ron: I THINK THAT ROSSIU HAS

00:07:20.413 --> 00:07:22.451
SOMETHING UP HIS SLEEVE.

00:07:22.451 --> 00:07:24.421
ANYWAY, WE CAN’T WORRY

00:07:24.421 --> 00:07:24.889
ABOUT THAT.

00:07:24.889 --> 00:07:26.994
OUR TASK AT HAND IS DEVELOPING

00:07:26.994 --> 00:07:28.463
WEAPONS AGAINST OUR NEW ENEMIES.

00:07:28.463 --> 00:07:29.198
&gt;&gt; Tetsukan: I GUESS IT’S NO

00:07:29.198 --> 00:07:30.568
SLEEP FOR US UNTIL WE

00:07:30.568 --> 00:07:31.670
COME UP WITH SOMETHING.

00:07:31.670 --> 00:07:33.641
&gt;&gt; Ron: ARTENBOROUGH, TURN THIS

00:07:33.641 --> 00:07:34.776
NEW REPORT IN TO ROSSIU,

00:07:34.776 --> 00:07:35.443
WOULD YOU?

00:07:35.443 --> 00:07:37.815
&gt;&gt; Artenborough: YOU GOT IT!

00:07:37.815 --> 00:07:38.784
[yelping]

00:07:38.784 --> 00:07:41.823
&gt;&gt; Ron: WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!

00:07:41.823 --> 00:07:43.459
I ASKED YOU TO TURN IN THE

00:07:43.459 --> 00:07:45.196
REPORT, NOT TURN ME!

00:07:45.196 --> 00:07:47.234
WAIT! TURNING...

00:07:47.234 --> 00:07:49.038
COULD IT REALLY BE?

00:07:49.038 --> 00:07:50.508
ARTENBOROUGH, SHOW US

00:07:50.508 --> 00:07:50.941
THAT IMAGE AGAIN!

00:07:50.941 --> 00:07:52.177
&gt;&gt; Artenborough: YOU GOT IT!

00:07:52.177 --> 00:07:54.849
&gt;&gt; Ron: WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

00:07:54.849 --> 00:07:57.588
THAT’S NOT WHAT I ASKED YOU!

00:08:00.193 --> 00:08:01.697
&gt;&gt; Guinble: WE’VE COMPLETED

00:08:01.697 --> 00:08:02.765
SURVEYING THE SURVIVING

00:08:02.765 --> 00:08:06.606
UNDERGROUND CITIES.

00:08:06.606 --> 00:08:07.709
SCATTERED AROUND THE WORLD,

00:08:07.709 --> 00:08:10.246
THERE ARE 36 CITIES OVER 1,000

00:08:10.246 --> 00:08:12.084
METERS UNDERGROUND, EACH CAPABLE

00:08:12.084 --> 00:08:13.486
OF WITHSTANDING THE LUNAR

00:08:13.486 --> 00:08:14.556
IMPACT.

00:08:14.556 --> 00:08:15.758
ALL TOGETHER, THEY CAN HOLD

00:08:15.758 --> 00:08:18.162
UP TO 640,000 PEOPLE.

00:08:18.162 --> 00:08:19.599
&gt;&gt; Kinon: GREAT NEWS.

00:08:19.599 --> 00:08:20.768
THAT’S SO MUCH MORE THAN WE

00:08:20.768 --> 00:08:21.937
EXPECTED.

00:08:21.937 --> 00:08:22.905
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: I SUPPOSE THAT WE

00:08:22.905 --> 00:08:23.941
OWE A DEBT OF GRATITUDE

00:08:23.941 --> 00:08:25.511
TO THE HUMANS OF THE PAST

00:08:25.511 --> 00:08:27.114
WHOSE CIVILIZATIONS SO EXCELLED.

00:08:27.114 --> 00:08:28.617
&gt;&gt; Guinble: EVEN SO, THOSE

00:08:28.617 --> 00:08:29.853
HUMANS AND THEIR CIVILIZATIONS

00:08:29.853 --> 00:08:30.888
WERE NO MATCH FOR THE

00:08:30.888 --> 00:08:33.493
ANTI‐SPIRALS.

00:08:33.493 --> 00:08:34.495
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: NEVERTHELESS,

00:08:34.495 --> 00:08:35.497
WE WILL SURVIVE...

00:08:35.497 --> 00:08:37.935
BY ANY MEANS NECESSARY.

00:08:37.935 --> 00:08:40.240
&gt;&gt; Kinon: 360,000 TO GO.

00:08:40.240 --> 00:08:42.077
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: I KNOW.

00:08:42.077 --> 00:08:43.747
THE CITIZENS HERE IN KAMINA CITY

00:08:43.747 --> 00:08:44.616
WILL BE QUITE DIFFICULT.

00:08:44.616 --> 00:08:45.918
&gt;&gt; ADVISOR ROSSIU!

00:08:45.918 --> 00:08:47.054
I FOUND THIS FILE IN THE

00:08:47.054 --> 00:08:48.524
BIOCOMPUTER’S DEEP‐LEVEL

00:08:48.524 --> 00:08:49.592
DATABASE.

00:08:49.592 --> 00:08:50.761
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: WHAT IN THE WORLD?

00:08:50.761 --> 00:08:51.863
WHERE IS IT?!

00:08:51.863 --> 00:08:53.232
&gt;&gt; RIGHT UNDERNEATH KAMINA

00:08:53.232 --> 00:08:57.775
CITY’S PARLIAMENT TOWER.

00:09:04.154 --> 00:09:05.825
&gt;&gt; Kinon: AMAZING!

00:09:05.825 --> 00:09:07.027
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: LEAVE IT TO THE

00:09:07.027 --> 00:09:07.929
SPIRAL KING.

00:09:07.929 --> 00:09:09.966
HE HAD THIS CARD UP HIS SLEEVE

00:09:09.966 --> 00:09:12.605
THE WHOLE TIME.

00:09:13.907 --> 00:09:17.949
♪ ROW, ROW, FIGHT THE POWER ♪ ♪

00:09:20.988 --> 00:09:23.861
♪ ROW, ROW, FIGHT THE POWER ♪ ♪

00:09:27.535 --> 00:09:30.006
[pounds gavel twice]

00:09:30.006 --> 00:09:31.041
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: I WILL HAND DOWN

00:09:31.041 --> 00:09:32.177
THE SENTENCE.

00:09:32.177 --> 00:09:33.881
SIMON, IS HEREBY CONDEMNED

00:09:33.881 --> 00:09:35.250
TO DEATH.

00:09:35.250 --> 00:09:36.252
[commotion, shouting]

00:09:36.252 --> 00:09:36.853
&gt;&gt; Kittan: WHAT!

00:09:36.853 --> 00:09:38.791
HEY, HOLD ON JUST A SECOND!

00:09:38.791 --> 00:09:39.893
&gt;&gt; Zorthy: GET REAL!

00:09:39.893 --> 00:09:40.761
&gt;&gt; WHAT THE HELL?

00:09:40.761 --> 00:09:41.763
&gt;&gt; Jorgun: THIS DON’T MAKE

00:09:41.763 --> 00:09:44.101
NO SENSE!

00:09:44.101 --> 00:09:45.270
&gt;&gt; Kittan: FIRST OF ALL, IT WAS

00:09:45.270 --> 00:09:47.809
CRAZY TO MAKE BALINBOW SIMON’S

00:09:47.809 --> 00:09:49.612
DEFENSE ATTORNEY!

00:09:49.612 --> 00:09:51.115
AND GUINBLE WAS THE PROSECUTOR,

00:09:51.115 --> 00:09:53.052
AND YOU WERE THE JUDGE!

00:09:53.052 --> 00:09:54.054
YOU HAD NO INTENTION WHATSOEVER

00:09:54.054 --> 00:09:56.292
OF GIVING SIMON A FAIR TRIAL!

00:09:56.292 --> 00:09:57.194
[pounds gavel]

00:09:57.194 --> 00:09:58.630
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: QUIET IN MY

00:09:58.630 --> 00:10:00.300
COURTROOM, LEGAL AFFAIRS CHIEF

00:10:00.300 --> 00:10:01.168
KITTAN.

00:10:01.168 --> 00:10:02.137
IF WE DON’T SHOW WE’RE WILLING

00:10:02.137 --> 00:10:03.072
TO HOLD SOMEONE RESPONSIBLE,

00:10:03.072 --> 00:10:05.210
THE POPULACE WON’T BE SATISFIED.

00:10:05.210 --> 00:10:06.112
WHO DO YOU SUGGEST WE HOLD

00:10:06.112 --> 00:10:07.114
RESPONSIBLE, IF NOT SUPREME

00:10:07.114 --> 00:10:09.218
COMMANDER SIMON?

00:10:09.218 --> 00:10:10.353
&gt;&gt; Kittan: THAT DOESN’T MEAN

00:10:10.353 --> 00:10:11.055
YOU HAVE TO HAVE HIM

00:10:11.055 --> 00:10:12.758
PUT TO DEATH!

00:10:12.758 --> 00:10:14.128
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: THIS MAY QUIET DOWN

00:10:14.128 --> 00:10:15.130
THE UNREST FOR NOW, BUT WHAT

00:10:15.130 --> 00:10:16.666
ABOUT AFTERWARDS?

00:10:16.666 --> 00:10:17.668
WHAT DO YOU PLAN TO DO ABOUT

00:10:17.668 --> 00:10:19.171
THE FALLING MOON?

00:10:19.171 --> 00:10:20.240
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: AN EVACUATION PLAN IS

00:10:20.240 --> 00:10:21.943
ALREADY UNDER WAY.

00:10:21.943 --> 00:10:23.312
TO ENSURE HUMANITY’S SURVIVAL,

00:10:23.312 --> 00:10:25.150
WE MUST QUELL THIS FOOLISH

00:10:25.150 --> 00:10:27.788
DISTURBANCE AT ONCE AND THEN

00:10:27.788 --> 00:10:29.626
TAKE CALM, SWIFT ACTION.

00:10:29.626 --> 00:10:30.961
&gt;&gt; Guinble: WITH CHIEF ADVISOR‐‐

00:10:30.961 --> 00:10:33.032
NO, NEW SUPREME COMMANDER

00:10:33.032 --> 00:10:35.069
ROSSIU AT THE HELM.

00:10:35.069 --> 00:10:36.940
[commotion]

00:10:36.940 --> 00:10:37.942
&gt;&gt; Kittan: NEW SUPREME

00:10:37.942 --> 00:10:38.944
COMMANDER?

00:10:38.944 --> 00:10:39.879
IS THIS SOME KIND OF COUP,

00:10:39.879 --> 00:10:40.948
ROSSIU?

00:10:40.948 --> 00:10:41.950
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: THIS IS NOTHING OF

00:10:41.950 --> 00:10:42.618
THE SORT.

00:10:42.618 --> 00:10:45.223
ACCORDING TO THE LAW, THE

00:10:45.223 --> 00:10:46.827
INSTANT SIMON WAS FOUND GUILTY,

00:10:46.827 --> 00:10:48.062
I SUCCEEDED HIM.

00:10:48.062 --> 00:10:49.331
&gt;&gt; Simon: BRO...

00:10:49.331 --> 00:10:50.133
IF YOU WERE IN MY SHOES,

00:10:50.133 --> 00:10:56.278
WHAT WOULD YOU DO?

00:10:56.278 --> 00:10:57.982
NIA!

00:10:57.982 --> 00:10:59.652
[commotion]

00:10:59.652 --> 00:11:01.656
&gt;&gt; HOW’D SHE GET HERE?

00:11:01.656 --> 00:11:03.226
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: HEY, IT’S NIA!

00:11:03.226 --> 00:11:04.361
&gt;&gt; Kittan: IS THIS FOR REAL?!

00:11:04.361 --> 00:11:05.363
&gt;&gt; Zorthy: WHERE’D SHE COME

00:11:05.363 --> 00:11:06.933
FROM?

00:11:06.933 --> 00:11:09.371
&gt;&gt; Nia: WHAT THE ANTI‐SPIRALS

00:11:09.371 --> 00:11:12.043
WANT IS ABSOLUTE DESPAIR.

00:11:12.043 --> 00:11:13.246
SPIRAL LIFE HAS NO HOPE

00:11:13.246 --> 00:11:14.147
OF SURVIVAL.

00:11:14.147 --> 00:11:15.183
&gt;&gt; Simon: NIA! WHAT ARE YOU

00:11:15.183 --> 00:11:16.018
TALKING ABOUT?

00:11:16.018 --> 00:11:17.053
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,

00:11:17.053 --> 00:11:18.222
ABSOLUTE DESPAIR?

00:11:18.222 --> 00:11:19.224
WHY ARE YOU DOING THIS

00:11:19.224 --> 00:11:21.930
TERRIBLE THING?!

00:11:21.930 --> 00:11:23.734
[Simon grunting]

00:11:23.734 --> 00:11:25.804
&gt;&gt; Nia: FOR THE NEXT TWO WEEKS,

00:11:25.804 --> 00:11:28.309
MEET YOUR END IN SUFFERING AS

00:11:28.309 --> 00:11:34.354
YOU CLING DESPERATELY TO LIFE.

00:11:34.354 --> 00:11:36.826
&gt;&gt; Simon: NIA, DON’T GO!

00:11:36.826 --> 00:11:41.068
[alarm blaring]

00:11:41.068 --> 00:11:42.204
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: CYBELA!

00:11:42.204 --> 00:11:43.172
WHAT’S HAPPENING?

00:11:43.172 --> 00:11:44.041
&gt;&gt; Cybela: I’M DETECTING

00:11:44.041 --> 00:11:45.744
A MUGANN ABOVE PLANNED SHELTER

00:11:45.744 --> 00:11:46.312
AREA LITTNER.

00:11:46.312 --> 00:11:47.414
IT’S A LOT LARGER THAN ANY WE’VE

00:11:47.414 --> 00:11:48.382
SEEN BEFORE.

00:11:48.382 --> 00:11:55.029
[alarm blaring]

00:12:01.475 --> 00:12:03.079
&gt;&gt; TH‐THIS IS LITTNER SECTOR!

00:12:03.079 --> 00:12:04.916
A HUGE CLUMP OF MUGANN IS

00:12:04.916 --> 00:12:06.352
HEADING THIS WAY!

00:12:06.352 --> 00:12:09.124
[weapons firing on broadcast]

00:12:09.124 --> 00:12:12.030
AGH! WE’RE UNDER ATTACK!

00:12:12.030 --> 00:12:13.132
THEY’RE PULLING OUT ALL

00:12:13.132 --> 00:12:14.134
THE STOPS!

00:12:14.134 --> 00:12:16.205
THE SHELTER CAN’T TAKE THIS!

00:12:16.205 --> 00:12:18.309
REQUESTING IMMEDIATE ASSISTANCE!

00:12:18.309 --> 00:12:19.444
HELP US!

00:12:19.444 --> 00:12:20.346
[scream cuts off]

00:12:20.346 --> 00:12:21.081
[commotion]

00:12:21.081 --> 00:12:22.183
&gt;&gt; Guinble: APPARENTLY THE

00:12:22.183 --> 00:12:23.720
MUGANN HAVE BEGUN MOVING

00:12:23.720 --> 00:12:27.762
TOWARDS KAMINA CITY, SIR.

00:12:27.762 --> 00:12:31.001
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: WHAT OF LITTNER?

00:12:31.001 --> 00:12:35.076
WHAT’S HAPPENED TO LITTNER?

00:12:35.076 --> 00:12:36.278
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: BACK TO THE

00:12:36.278 --> 00:12:37.848
OPERATIONS ROOM AT ONCE!

00:12:37.848 --> 00:12:40.521
&gt;&gt; Simon: ROSSIU, WAIT.

00:12:40.521 --> 00:12:42.223
I WANT YOU TO LET ME GO OUT AND

00:12:42.223 --> 00:12:43.192
PILOT GURREN LAGANN.

00:12:43.192 --> 00:12:44.996
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: WHAT DID YOU

00:12:44.996 --> 00:12:45.831
JUST SAY?

00:12:45.831 --> 00:12:47.133
&gt;&gt; Simon: THERE’S ONE WAY FOR US

00:12:47.133 --> 00:12:48.102
TO FIGHT THESE THINGS, AND

00:12:48.102 --> 00:12:49.171
THAT’S GURREN LAGANN.

00:12:49.171 --> 00:12:49.939
YOU KNOW THAT.

00:12:49.939 --> 00:12:51.108
&gt;&gt; Guinble: TRYING TO REDEEM

00:12:51.108 --> 00:12:52.010
YOURSELF THROUGH A NOBLE

00:12:52.010 --> 00:12:53.346
ACT OF HEROISM, ARE YOU?

00:12:53.346 --> 00:12:54.314
&gt;&gt; Simon: NO, THAT’S NOT IT!

00:12:54.314 --> 00:12:55.784
I JUST WANT TO BE ABLE

00:12:55.784 --> 00:12:56.385
TO PROTECT THE CITY!

00:12:56.385 --> 00:12:57.253
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: YOU ARE

00:12:57.253 --> 00:12:58.289
A CONDEMNED MAN.

00:12:58.289 --> 00:12:59.291
AM I SUPPOSED TO ENTRUST A

00:12:59.291 --> 00:13:00.393
PRISONER WITH GURREN LAGANN WHEN

00:13:00.393 --> 00:13:03.199
HE MIGHT ESCAPE IN IT?

00:13:03.199 --> 00:13:04.334
&gt;&gt; Kittan: YOU SON OF A BITCH!

00:13:04.334 --> 00:13:05.336
&gt;&gt; Simon: WELL, THEN JUST WIRE

00:13:05.336 --> 00:13:06.338
ME WITH A WHOLE BUNCH OF

00:13:06.338 --> 00:13:07.173
EXPLOSIVES!

00:13:07.173 --> 00:13:08.042
IF I RUN, ALL YOU’LL HAVE TO DO

00:13:08.042 --> 00:13:11.115
IS DETONATE IT!

00:13:21.135 --> 00:13:23.005
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: GUINBLE.

00:13:23.005 --> 00:13:24.174
&gt;&gt; Guinble: SIR.

00:13:24.174 --> 00:13:25.143
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: DISENGAGE THE LOCK

00:13:25.143 --> 00:13:27.480
ON THE CORE DRILL STOREROOM.

00:13:27.480 --> 00:13:28.215
AND DON’T FORGET TO WIRE

00:13:28.215 --> 00:13:29.318
GURREN WITH EXPLOSIVES.

00:13:29.318 --> 00:13:34.094
DO IT AT ONCE!

00:13:34.094 --> 00:13:35.229
&gt;&gt; Simon: GURREN LAGANN

00:13:35.229 --> 00:13:36.432
HEADING OUT!

00:13:36.432 --> 00:13:37.802
&gt;&gt; Kinon: ROGER THAT.

00:13:37.802 --> 00:13:38.402
I AM STANDING BY AND READY

00:13:38.402 --> 00:13:39.839
TO GO.

00:13:39.839 --> 00:13:40.440
&gt;&gt; Simon: KINON?

00:13:40.440 --> 00:13:41.375
WHAT ARE YOU DOING ABOARD

00:13:41.375 --> 00:13:42.444
GURREN?

00:13:42.444 --> 00:13:43.346
&gt;&gt; Kinon: I WIRED THE DETONATOR

00:13:43.346 --> 00:13:44.448
SWITCH FOR THE EXPLOSIVES

00:13:44.448 --> 00:13:45.584
TO MY BELT, SIMON.

00:13:45.584 --> 00:13:46.986
&gt;&gt; Simon: WHAT?

00:13:46.986 --> 00:13:47.387
&gt;&gt; Kinon: PLEASE,

00:13:47.387 --> 00:13:48.189
I’M WARNING YOU.

00:13:48.189 --> 00:13:49.224
IF YOU TRY ANYTHING FUNNY,

00:13:49.224 --> 00:13:50.561
ANYTHING AT ALL, I WILL NOT

00:13:50.561 --> 00:13:51.830
HESITATE TO HIT THE SWITCH.

00:13:51.830 --> 00:13:52.497
&gt;&gt; Simon: THIS IS CRAZY!

00:13:52.497 --> 00:13:53.399
WHAT DO YOU THINK

00:13:53.399 --> 00:13:54.334
YOU’RE DOING?

00:13:54.334 --> 00:13:55.838
WHY THE HELL DOES KINON HAVE

00:13:55.838 --> 00:13:57.107
TO COME ALONG WITH ME ON THIS?!

00:13:57.107 --> 00:13:58.042
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: WITH HER ABOARD,

00:13:58.042 --> 00:13:59.011
YOU’LL HAVE NO CHOICE BUT

00:13:59.011 --> 00:14:00.413
TO RETURN TO BASE INTACT.

00:14:00.413 --> 00:14:01.983
GOING BY YOURSELF, I WOULD

00:14:01.983 --> 00:14:02.985
EXPECT YOU TO TRY AND FIND SOME

00:14:02.985 --> 00:14:05.223
WAY TO GO OUT IN A HEROIC BLAZE

00:14:05.223 --> 00:14:05.824
OF GLORY.

00:14:05.824 --> 00:14:07.260
&gt;&gt; Simon: THAT DOESN’T MEAN YOU

00:14:07.260 --> 00:14:08.262
NEED TO PUT HER LIFE AT RISK

00:14:08.262 --> 00:14:08.964
LIKE THIS, ROSSIU!

00:14:08.964 --> 00:14:10.266
&gt;&gt; Kinon: I VOLUNTEERED

00:14:10.266 --> 00:14:11.101
TO DO THIS.

00:14:11.101 --> 00:14:12.270
&gt;&gt; Simon: KINON?

00:14:12.270 --> 00:14:13.205
&gt;&gt; Kinon: IT’S ALL RIGHT.

00:14:13.205 --> 00:14:14.307
IF WE MAKE IT BACK,

00:14:14.307 --> 00:14:17.047
THERE WON’T BE ANY TROUBLE.

00:14:17.047 --> 00:14:18.282
&gt;&gt; Simon: COME HOME SAFE AND

00:14:18.282 --> 00:14:19.317
SOUND SO I CAN BE PUT

00:14:19.317 --> 00:14:21.255
TO DEATH PROPERLY?

00:14:21.255 --> 00:14:21.856
LET’S GO!

00:14:21.856 --> 00:14:24.127
&gt;&gt; Kinon: OKAY!

00:14:28.402 --> 00:14:29.906
&gt;&gt; Guinble: COMMANDER ROSSIU,

00:14:29.906 --> 00:14:32.043
WE ARE READY FOR YOUR BROADCAST.

00:14:32.043 --> 00:14:35.183
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: GOOD.

00:14:35.183 --> 00:14:36.920
&gt;&gt; HEY, HEY, AIN’T THAT GURREN

00:14:36.920 --> 00:14:38.289
LAGANN UP THERE?

00:14:38.289 --> 00:14:39.291
&gt;&gt; I THOUGHT SIMON WAS ARRESTED

00:14:39.291 --> 00:14:40.393
LAST NIGHT.

00:14:40.393 --> 00:14:41.996
WHAT’S GOING ON HERE?

00:14:41.996 --> 00:14:44.434
[chime rings]

00:14:44.434 --> 00:14:45.604
&gt;&gt; announcer: STAND BY FOR AN

00:14:45.604 --> 00:14:46.438
URGENT GOVERNMENT MESSAGE.

00:14:46.438 --> 00:14:48.142
I REPEAT, STAND BY FOR AN

00:14:48.142 --> 00:14:50.113
URGENT GOVERNMENT MESSAGE.

00:14:50.113 --> 00:14:51.215
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: FELLOW CITIZENS,

00:14:51.215 --> 00:14:52.383
A GROUP CALLING THEMSELVES THE

00:14:52.383 --> 00:14:53.319
ANTI‐SPIRALS WILL SOON DAMAGE

00:14:53.319 --> 00:14:55.356
EARTH’S SURFACE...

00:14:55.356 --> 00:14:56.593
BY CAUSING THE MOON TO FALL AND

00:14:56.593 --> 00:14:58.329
CRASH INTO OUR PLANET.

00:14:58.329 --> 00:14:59.599
IN RESPONSE TO THIS NEWS,

00:14:59.599 --> 00:15:01.301
THE NEW GOVERNMENT PRESSED

00:15:01.301 --> 00:15:02.872
CHARGES AGAINST FORMER COMMANDER

00:15:02.872 --> 00:15:03.640
SIMON.

00:15:03.640 --> 00:15:05.309
AS A RESULT OF HIS TRIAL TODAY,

00:15:05.309 --> 00:15:08.249
HE WAS SENTENCED TO DEATH.

00:15:08.249 --> 00:15:10.621
&gt;&gt; Simon: THERE IT IS!

00:15:10.621 --> 00:15:12.323
I’M NOT LETTING THAT THING GET

00:15:12.323 --> 00:15:15.631
ANYWHERE NEAR KAMINA CITY!

00:15:15.631 --> 00:15:17.333
I’LL STOP IT HERE,

00:15:17.333 --> 00:15:19.337
WHATEVER IT TAKES!

00:15:19.337 --> 00:15:20.607
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: I HAVE RECENTLY

00:15:20.607 --> 00:15:21.676
DISPATCHED FORMER COMMANDER

00:15:21.676 --> 00:15:23.012
SIMON IN GURREN LAGANN TO

00:15:23.012 --> 00:15:24.347
INTERCEPT THE MUGANN THAT HAVE

00:15:24.347 --> 00:15:26.018
APPEARED OUTSIDE KAMINA CITY.

00:15:26.018 --> 00:15:28.055
BUT I WANT TO ASSURE YOU HE IS

00:15:28.055 --> 00:15:29.124
COMPLETELY UNDER THE NEW

00:15:29.124 --> 00:15:30.226
GOVERNMENT’S CONTROL.

00:15:30.226 --> 00:15:31.663
WE ARE ABLE TO BLOW UP GURREN

00:15:31.663 --> 00:15:32.998
LAGANN SHOULD HE EXHIBIT ANY

00:15:32.998 --> 00:15:35.336
SUSPICIOUS BEHAVIOR WHATSOEVER.

00:15:35.336 --> 00:15:36.305
&gt;&gt; Kiyal: OH, SON OF A‐‐

00:15:36.305 --> 00:15:37.641
ROSSIU, YOU JERK!

00:15:37.641 --> 00:15:39.044
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: TO PROTECT ITS

00:15:39.044 --> 00:15:39.946
CITIZENS FROM THE IMPENDING

00:15:39.946 --> 00:15:40.914
LUNAR IMPACT, THE GOVERNMENT

00:15:40.914 --> 00:15:41.583
WILL CARRY OUT A LARGE‐SCALE

00:15:41.583 --> 00:15:43.285
EVACUATION.

00:15:43.285 --> 00:15:44.321
CITIZENS AROUND THE WORLD WILL

00:15:44.321 --> 00:15:46.125
BE EVACUATED TO 36 GIANT

00:15:46.125 --> 00:15:47.494
UNDERGROUND SHELTERS.

00:15:47.494 --> 00:15:48.663
RESIDENTS OF KAMINA CITY, WHICH

00:15:48.663 --> 00:15:51.168
HAS NO SHELTER, WILL TEMPORARILY

00:15:51.168 --> 00:15:52.638
LEAVE THE PLANET’S STRATOSPHERE

00:15:52.638 --> 00:15:54.274
IN THE SUPER DREADNAUGHT

00:15:54.274 --> 00:15:55.577
SPACE DAI‐GUN.

00:15:55.577 --> 00:15:57.413
I GIVE YOU THAT SPACE DAI‐GUN.

00:15:57.413 --> 00:16:00.419
BEHOLD ARC‐GURREN!

00:16:07.233 --> 00:16:08.970
[commotion]

00:16:08.970 --> 00:16:10.273
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: HAVE FAITH IN THE NEW

00:16:10.273 --> 00:16:10.974
GOVERNMENT!

00:16:10.974 --> 00:16:12.477
THE ANTI‐SPIRALS WON’T WIN!

00:16:12.477 --> 00:16:14.080
NO MATTER WHAT THEY TRY TO DO,

00:16:14.080 --> 00:16:15.383
WE’LL SURVIVE!

00:16:15.383 --> 00:16:17.320
[cheering]

00:16:17.320 --> 00:16:21.596
[chanting, "Rossiu"]

00:16:21.596 --> 00:16:23.499
&gt;&gt; YEAH! ALL RIGHT!

00:16:23.499 --> 00:16:27.608
&gt;&gt; THIS WILL KEEP US ALIVE!

00:16:27.608 --> 00:16:31.348
[chanting, "Rossiu"]

00:16:38.563 --> 00:16:39.599
&gt;&gt; Kinon: SIMON!

00:16:39.599 --> 00:16:41.068
THE MUGANN HAVE TURNED AROUND

00:16:41.068 --> 00:16:43.272
AND ARE NOW HEADING THIS WAY!

00:16:43.272 --> 00:16:44.107
&gt;&gt; Simon: THAT’S WHAT I WANT.

00:16:44.107 --> 00:16:45.343
NOW LET’S DRAW THEM AWAY FROM

00:16:45.343 --> 00:16:48.517
THE CITY!

00:16:48.517 --> 00:16:50.186
THESE GUYS ARE PRETTY SLOW.

00:16:50.186 --> 00:16:51.221
BRING THE SPEED DOWN SO THEY

00:16:51.221 --> 00:16:52.390
CAN KEEP UP.

00:16:52.390 --> 00:16:54.094
&gt;&gt; Kinon: RIGHT!

00:16:54.094 --> 00:16:54.529
&gt;&gt; Simon: THE BEAMS

00:16:54.529 --> 00:16:57.635
HAVE STOPPED.

00:17:02.377 --> 00:17:03.580
AH, NOW THEY’RE JUST

00:17:03.580 --> 00:17:05.584
SHOWING OFF.

00:17:12.363 --> 00:17:13.633
NOT GOOD.

00:17:13.633 --> 00:17:15.102
THESE THINGS HAVE GOT US HEADING

00:17:15.102 --> 00:17:16.305
TOWARDS KAMINA CITY AGAIN!

00:17:16.305 --> 00:17:17.373
&gt;&gt; Kinon: SIMON!

00:17:17.373 --> 00:17:18.475
THAT BIG MUGANN UP THERE HAS

00:17:18.475 --> 00:17:19.411
STAYED AT A DISTANCE THIS WHOLE

00:17:19.411 --> 00:17:20.547
TIME!

00:17:20.547 --> 00:17:21.649
IT’S POSSIBLE THAT IT’S THEIR

00:17:21.649 --> 00:17:22.785
CONTROL TOWER!

00:17:22.785 --> 00:17:24.054
&gt;&gt; Simon: I FOLLOW YOU.

00:17:24.054 --> 00:17:27.193
LET’S TEST THAT OUT!

00:17:45.162 --> 00:17:47.735
YOU ARE MINE!

00:17:49.304 --> 00:17:50.273
NIA!

00:17:50.273 --> 00:17:53.245
&gt;&gt; Nia: GOOD‐BYE, SIMON.

00:17:58.155 --> 00:18:00.560
&gt;&gt; Simon: UGH! WE’RE SURROUNDED!

00:18:00.560 --> 00:18:01.663
&gt;&gt; Kinon: IF THIS MANY FIRE

00:18:01.663 --> 00:18:02.531
AT US AT ONCE, ONE GIGA DRILL

00:18:02.531 --> 00:18:04.334
WON’T BE ENOUGH TO DEFLECT

00:18:04.334 --> 00:18:04.769
THEM ALL!

00:18:04.769 --> 00:18:06.071
&gt;&gt; Simon: THEN WE’LL JUST HAVE

00:18:06.071 --> 00:18:08.409
TO USE MORE THAN ONE!

00:18:08.409 --> 00:18:10.681
GIGA...

00:18:10.681 --> 00:18:13.419
DRILL...

00:18:13.419 --> 00:18:15.456
